s://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/ffmpeg/", "title": "ffmpeg", "content_html": "<h1>ffmpeg</h1>\n<p>```tldr\n  Video conversion tool.\n  More information: <a href=\"https://ffmpeg.org\">https://ffmpeg.org</a>.</p>\n<p>Extract the sound from a video and save it as MP3:</p>\n<pre><code>  ffmpeg -i p...\n</code></pre>", "image": null, "date_published": "2025-06-17T00:00:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/taskwarrior/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/taskwarrior/", "title": "taskwarrior", "content_html": "<h1>taskwarrior</h1>\n<h2>overview</h2>\n<p>Command-line to-do list manager. <a href=\"https://taskwarrior.org/docs/\">More information</a>.</p>\n<p>```\n  Add a new task which is due tomorrow:\n...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2025-06-17T00:00:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/linux/fhs/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/linux/fhs/", "title": "Filesystem Hierarchy Standard", "content_html": "<h1>Filesystem Hierarchy Standard</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/FHS_3.0/fhs/index.html\">standard ref</a></p>\n<p>This standard consists of a set of requirements...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2025-06-09T00:00:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/pake/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/pake/", "title": "pake\u6253\u5305web\u5e94\u7528", "content_html": "<h1>pake\u6253\u5305web\u5e94\u7528</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake\">pake</a>\u53ef\u4ee5\u5c06web\u8f6c\u5316\u4e3a\u684c\u9762\u5e94\u7528\uff0c\u6bd4<code>electron</code>\u66f4\u8f7b\u91cf\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u5b89\u88c5pake</h2>\n<p>\u7528\u6237\u7ea7\u5b89\u88c5\uff1a</p>\n<p><code>npm -g install pake-cli</code></p>\n<p>\u9700\u8981<code>rust</code>\u7b49\u5de5\u5177\u94fe</p>\n<h2>\u6253\u5305web\u5e94...</h2>", "image": null, "date_published": "2025-06-08T00:00: